<entry>
<author><name><![CDATA[AbuKhuzaimahAnsari]]></name></author>
<updated>2017-03-09T21:25:55+01:00</updated>
<published>2017-03-09T21:25:55+01:00</published>
<id>https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=963&amp;p=1342#p1342</id>
<link href="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=963&amp;p=1342#p1342"/>
<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: 999 Statements In Defence of the Salafi Creed and Manhaj]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=963&amp;p=1342#p1342"><![CDATA[
<strong>999 Statements In Defence of the Salafi Creed and Manhaj<br /><br />-19-</strong><br /><br /><blockquote class="uncited"><div><br />It is reported from al-Abbâs bin al-Waleed that ‘Uqbah said: “I was once with Arta’ah bin al-Mundhir when one of the people in the gathering said, “What do you say about a man who sits with the followers of the Sunnah and mixes with them, but when the followers of Bid’ah are mentioned he says, ‘Spare us from mentioning them, do not talk about them?’” Arta’ah said, “He is one of them, do not let him confuse you about his condition.” I felt this was strange, so I went to al-Awzaa’ee – and he used to clarify these matters when they came to him. He said, “Arta’ah is right, the matter is as he said; this person forbids talking about [Ahlal-Bid’ah], so how can [people] be on guard against them if they are not exposed?” (Ibn ‘Asâkir, Târîkh Dimishq 8:15)<br /></div></blockquote><br /><br /><strong>BENEFITS</strong><br /><br />1.Unfortunately, a severe illness has crept in amongst general people today and the people are told that to refute is not the correct way and that this hardens the heart and causes harshness and so on. So consider the aforementioned statement, and consider it over and over again for it encapsulates the manhaj of the salaf, who were the most balanced and kindest of people. <br /><br /><br /><span style="color: #0000BF">www.salafiri.com</span><br /><span style="color: #BF8000">www.forum.salafiri.com  </span>    <br /><span style="color: #FF0000">www.salafiri.bigcartel.com</span><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://twitter.com/salafiri_com">http://twitter.com/salafiri_com</a><!-- m --><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.facebook.com/Salafiri">https://www.facebook.com/Salafiri</a><!-- m --><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=48">AbuKhuzaimahAnsari</a> — Thu Mar 09, 2017 8:25 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
</entry>
<entry>
<author><name><![CDATA[AbuKhuzaimahAnsari]]></name></author>
<updated>2017-03-09T21:22:08+01:00</updated>
<published>2017-03-09T21:22:08+01:00</published>
<id>https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=963&amp;p=1341#p1341</id>
<link href="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=963&amp;p=1341#p1341"/>
<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: 999 Statements In Defence of the Salafi Creed and Manhaj]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=963&amp;p=1341#p1341"><![CDATA[
<strong>999 Statements In Defence of the Salafi Creed and Manhaj<br /><br />-18-</strong><br /><br /><blockquote class="uncited"><div><br />Imam Ibn Taymiyyah “Had Allah not made the upright repel the harm of the evil ones {i.e. Ahlul Bidah}, the religion would be corrupted and this corruption is far greater than that being caused when during war the people are conquered. Verily, when they take over a country they do not corrupt and take over the heart and that which is in it related to the deen, but they do it over a long period. On the other hand, the people of Bidah they corrupt the hearts from the outset.” (Majmoo al Fataawa 28:232) (taken from Oh Salafi do not drink from the Well..)<br /></div></blockquote><br /><br /><strong>BENEFITS</strong><br /><br />1. A profund and deep statement of Imam Taymiyyah in his understanding of the affairs of his time and how this pertinently relates to affairs in our times. <br /><br />2.Ahlul Bidah corrupt the din and the upright people repel and refute them.<br /><br />3. The corruption of Ahlul Bidah is far worse then the turmoil that proceeds when dealing with countries. <br /><br />4. Ahlul Bidah corrupt the people right from the beginning and this is the reason why the Salaf have mentioned numerous severe warnings with regards to having associations with the people of innovation and their underlings. <br /><br />5. The great importance in repelling falsehood and corruption of the people of misguidance and deviation which is to be done by the upright people and the are none other than the righteous and Scholars of Ahlus Sunnah. This also leads to the established principle of returning back the Scholars in all of the affairs and not the modern day quick buck speakers. Let alone those who have assumed authority over dawn and their words which they are not even qualified to say....<br /><br /><br /><span style="color: #0000BF">www.salafiri.com</span><br /><span style="color: #BF8000">www.forum.salafiri.com  </span>    <br /><span style="color: #FF0000">www.salafiri.bigcartel.com</span><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://twitter.com/salafiri_com">http://twitter.com/salafiri_com</a><!-- m --><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.facebook.com/Salafiri">https://www.facebook.com/Salafiri</a><!-- m --><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=48">AbuKhuzaimahAnsari</a> — Thu Mar 09, 2017 8:22 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
