<author><name><![CDATA[AbuKhuzaimahAnsari]]></name></author>
<updated>2017-03-09T21:19:22+01:00</updated>
<published>2017-03-09T21:19:22+01:00</published>
<id>https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=963&amp;p=1340#p1340</id>
<link href="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=963&amp;p=1340#p1340"/>
<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: 999 Statements In Defence of the Salafi Creed and Manhaj]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=963&amp;p=1340#p1340"><![CDATA[
<strong>999 Statements In Defence of the Salafi Creed and Manhaj<br /><br />-17-</strong><br /><br /><blockquote class="uncited"><div><br />Imam Ibn Taymiyyah“Some of the people said to Imaam Ahmad that ‘I find it difficult to criticise (narrators in the chain of narrations) that they have some problems and are like so and so? Imaam Ahmad replied, ‘if you and I remain silent, then how will the ignorant one know the authentic from the unauthentic narration?” (Majmoo al-Fataawa 28/231) (taken from Oh Salafi do not drink from the Well..)<br /></div></blockquote><br /><br /><strong>BENEFITS</strong><br /><br />1. The taqwa of the people during the time of Imam Ahmad.<br /><br />2. The permissibility and understanding of Imam Ahmad and the Salaf in refuting and speaking about the evilness and evil of the people who harm the din.<br /><br />3. Speaking about people who harm and misguide people in this Din is a must and infant one is aiding and helping the Muslims.<br /><br />4. It is not easy to criticise people but it must be done to make distinctions and uphold the vanguard of Islam.<br /><br />5. A lesson for the happy Muslims who are on this understanding, we are all Muslims and let us just unite and be happy!!!! Basically the Ikhwan and their modern day sympathisers and advocates.<br /><br /><br /><span style="color: #0000BF">www.salafiri.com</span><br /><span style="color: #BF8000">www.forum.salafiri.com  </span>    <br /><span style="color: #FF0000">www.salafiri.bigcartel.com</span><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://twitter.com/salafiri_com">http://twitter.com/salafiri_com</a><!-- m --><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.facebook.com/Salafiri">https://www.facebook.com/Salafiri</a><!-- m --><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=48">AbuKhuzaimahAnsari</a> — Thu Mar 09, 2017 8:19 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
