<author><name><![CDATA[AbuKhuzaimahAnsari]]></name></author>
<updated>2017-03-09T21:15:22+01:00</updated>
<published>2017-03-09T21:15:22+01:00</published>
<id>https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=963&amp;p=1339#p1339</id>
<link href="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=963&amp;p=1339#p1339"/>
<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: 999 Statements In Defence of the Salafi Creed and Manhaj]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=963&amp;p=1339#p1339"><![CDATA[
<strong>999 Statements In Defence of the Salafi Creed and Manhaj<br /><br />-16-</strong><br /><br /><blockquote class="uncited"><div><br />Imam Ibn Hazm (456H) said &quot;Hold on to the text which has been given to you from Rabb in the Quran and from your Prophet Sallalahu alayhi wasallam via trustworthy narrators from the scholars and Imams of the people of Hadith.&quot; (Kitab al-Fasl 2:116)<br /></div></blockquote><br /><br /><strong>BENEFITS</strong><br /><br />1. The obligation to accept everything from Quran and Hadith and acknowledging this to be mandatory in every aspect of the din, at the same token showing the significance and great importance of the fundamental sources of Islam.<br /><br />2. This is a clear and manifest refutation of taqlid and it's people ie the madhabists and Ghayr Ahlul Hadith.<br /><br />3. The scholars of Hadith and the Ahlul Hadith were stringent in narrating authentic ahadith.<br /><br />4. The scholars and imams were from amongst the Ahlul Hadith.<br /><br />5. The people of Hadith existed during he fifth 5th century of Islam way before the Ghayr Ahlul Hadith emerged ie the staunch madhabists.<br /><br /><br /><span style="color: #0000BF">www.salafiri.com</span><br /><span style="color: #BF8000">www.forum.salafiri.com  </span>    <br /><span style="color: #FF0000">www.salafiri.bigcartel.com</span><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://twitter.com/salafiri_com">http://twitter.com/salafiri_com</a><!-- m --><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.facebook.com/Salafiri">https://www.facebook.com/Salafiri</a><!-- m --><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=48">AbuKhuzaimahAnsari</a> — Thu Mar 09, 2017 8:15 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
