<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: 999 Statements In Defence of the Salafi Creed and Manhaj]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=963&amp;p=1337#p1337"><![CDATA[
<strong>999 Statements In Defence of the Salafi Creed and Manhaj<br /><br />-14-</strong><br /><br /><blockquote class="uncited"><div><br />Imam Ibn Qutaibah said, &quot;If someone was to ask about who Ahlus Sunnah are then surely the people would unhesitatingly say they are the Ahlul Hadith.&quot; (Tawil Mukhtalif al-Hadith pg.98)<br /></div></blockquote><br /><br /><strong>BENEFITS</strong><br /><br />1. Ahlus Sunnah are the Ahlul Hadith<br /><br />2. Even the average people knew who the Ahlul Hadith were and who Ahlus Sunnah were<br /><br /><br /><span style="color: #0000BF">www.salafiri.com</span><br /><span style="color: #BF8000">www.forum.salafiri.com  </span>    <br /><span style="color: #FF0000">www.salafiri.bigcartel.com</span><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://twitter.com/salafiri_com">http://twitter.com/salafiri_com</a><!-- m --><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.facebook.com/Salafiri">https://www.facebook.com/Salafiri</a><!-- m --><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=48">AbuKhuzaimahAnsari</a> — Thu Mar 09, 2017 8:07 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
